description: DNA Dynamics, Inc., through its subsidiaries, develops mobile applications and games for smartphones and tablet devices. It develops and publishes games for Apple iPhone/iPad/iPod touch and Android platforms; and develops video games and applications for mobile devices and handheld consoles. The company develops games across seven platforms, including titles for TV brands and intellectual property holders. DNA Dynamics, Inc. was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Leamington Spa, United Kingdom.
